    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've already missed a dose today cuz of the nausea and i'm feeling kinda jittery. i'm just worried that if i wait weeks for a doctor's appointment, my anxiety is gonna spike way worse. since st johns wort is just a plant and works on the same serotonin pathways, wouldn't it be fine to just start taking it right away to keep my levels steady? wont the herb just pick up where the zoloft left off?",
